          namespace: 'new_description',
          storefrontId: 'gid://shopify/Metafield/20236212830381',
          key: 'new_description',
          value:
            '<p>This lightweight serum expertly targets the appearance of dark spots, hyperpigmentation and dull skin, revealing a youthful glow and brightened complexion.</p>\n<p><span class="suitable">Suitable for:</span> dry, normal, combination, sensitive, mature skin</p>\n<div class="weight">1.6 fl oz / 47.5 ml</div>\n<div class="left_side">\n<h4>&gt;95%</h4>\n<p>of women said the texture of their skin appeared smoother and more radiant</p>\n<h4>&gt;95%</h4>\n<p>of participants agreed their skin appeared more luminous after just 7 days</p>\n<h4>100%</h4>\n<p>of women said their skin looked healthy and renewed after just 7 days</p>\n</div>\n<div class="questions">\n<div class="container">\n<h2>questions</h2>\n<div class="grid">\n<div class="grid__item large--two-thirds one-whole">\n<div class="grid question_list">\n<div class="grid__item one-half medium-down--one-whole question_item">\n<h5>Can I use both the Illuminating Serum and the Volume Defense Serum as part of my daily routine?</h5>\n<p>Absolutely. We recommend using the Illuminating Serum in the morning and the <a href="/products/volume-defense-deep-wrinkle-serum/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Volume Defense Serum</a> at night. In addition to promoting the appearance of even skin tone, the Illuminating Serum boosts radiance so that your skin will look bright and well-rested right after application. The Volume Defense Serum provides anti-aging benefits by reviving skin’s appearance while you sleep.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="grid__item one-half medium-down--one-whole question_item">\n<h5>Will this product help target my dark spots?</h5>\n<p>The Illuminating Face Serum is an excellent choice if dark spots, hyperpigmentation, and lackluster skin are your primary concerns. Our quick-absorbing serum works to brighten your complexion, help reduce the appearance of dark spots, and promote even skin tone.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class="benefits">\n<div class="one-whole">\n<div class="benefit_list"><h4>The benefits</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Evens skin tone, helps smooth texture and reduces the appearance of dark spots.</li>\n<li>Perfect under make-up to provide extra glow.</li>\n<li>Contains our signature probiotics to lock in moisture and leave skin looking nourished.</li>\n<li>Suitable for all skin types and all ages – especially for dull, lack-luster skin.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class="use_it">\n<div class="container">\n<div class="grid">\n<div class="how_use">\n<div class="grid__item  medium-down--one-whole four-twelfths">\n<h2>How to use</h2>\n<p>Apply a dime-sized amount onto clean skin in circular motions. Allow serum to absorb and then layer moisturizer on top.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="grid__item medium-down--one-whole  eight-twelfths">\n<div class="use_img"><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1736/9637/files/Illuminating-serum-HowToUse.jpg?v=1492692667" alt="Illuminating Serum" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class="inside">\n<div class="container">\n<div class="inside-content">\n<h2>WHAT’S INSIDE</h2>\n<div class="grid">\n<div class="grid__item one-third medium-large--two-quarters medium-down--one-whole">\n<ul class="ingredients-list">\n<li><strong>Tocopherol (Vitamin E) </strong>is an antioxidant that helps protect the skin and maintain a youthful appearance. </li>\n<li><strong>Citrus extracts and</strong> <strong>pearlescent pigments </strong>visibly<strong> </strong>brighten the skin and boost its radiance. </li>\n<li><strong>Safflower oil </strong>hydrates and leaves the skin looking supple and soft.</li>\n<li><strong>Chicory root </strong>is a natural anti-inflammatory prebiotic that helps boost the appearance of firmer skin.</li>\n<li><strong>Probiotics </strong>lock in moisture and support a balanced appearance.</li>\n</ul>\n<a class="i_link">See the full ingredients list</a></div>\n<div class="grid__item one-third medium-large--two-quarters medium-down--one-whole">\n<div class="probiotic-strains">\n<h5>Probiotic strains</h5>\n<ul>\n<li class="BFL">\n<h5>Bifida Ferment Lysate</h5>\n<p>Hydrates and locks in moisture.</p>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n<div class="free_from">\n<h5>free from</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1736/9637/files/free.png?v=1492495562" alt="Illuminating Serum" /><span>Sulfates</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div class="free-icon"><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1736/9637/files/free-icon.png?v=1492333395" alt="Illuminating Serum" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="grid__item one-third medium-large--two-quarters medium-down--one-whole">\n<div class="benefit_img"><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1736/9637/files/illuminating-serum-benefits.jpg?v=1492692728" alt="Illuminating Serum" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class="full_ingredient">\n<p>Aqua/Water/Eau, Glycerin, Citrus Unshiu Peel Extract, Propylene Glycol Dipelargonate, Aluminum Starch Octenylsuccinate, Dimethicone, Tribehenin PEG-20 Esters, Lactose, Milk Protein, Bifida Ferment Lysate, Yogurt Extract, Hydrolyzed Rice Protein, Cichorium Intybus (Chicory) Root Extract, Vaccinium Angustifolium (Blueberry) Fruit Extract, Olus/Vegetable Oil/Huile Végétale, Camelina Sativa Seed Oil, Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract, Curcuma Longa (Turmeric) Root Extract, Tocopheryl Acetate, Retinyl Palmitate, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Seed Oil, Xanthan Gum, Butylene Glycol, Pentylene Glycol, Caprylyl Glycol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Decylene Glycol, 1,2-Hexanediol, Bulnesia Sarmientoi Wood Oil, Citrus Limon (Lemon) Fruit Oil, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Oil, Juniperus Mexicana Oil, Cananga Odorata Flower Oil, Fragrance (Parfum), Sorbic Acid, Phenoxyethanol, Disodium EDTA, Mica, CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide).</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class="result_data">\n<h4>96%</h4>\n<p> of women said the serum left their skin looking more radiant and luminous after just 2 weeks.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class="results-note"><p>All results are based on a 4-week, independent, blind consumer use study of 23 women ages 25-60.</p></div>\n\n<div class="before_after">\n<div id="comparison_slide" style="background: url(\'//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1736/9637/files/after_1.jpg?v=1493120458\');">\n<div id="comparewrapper">\n<div id="divisor" style="background: url(\'//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1736/9637/files/before_1.jpg?v=1493120583\');"></div>\n</div>\n<input type="range" min="0" max="100" value="50" id="slider" oninput="moveDivisor()" /></div>\n</div>',
